      "parameters": {
        "width": 1680,
        "content": "## 📬 Need Help or Want to Customize This?\n📧 [robert@ynteractive.com](mailto:robert@ynteractive.com)  \n🔗 [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/robert-breen-29429625/)"
